# ─── Anti-Cruft: block agent-dropped one-offs ───
# Agents create test directories, review dumps, and one-off scripts in root.
# All temporary work goes to /tmp/ (workspace rule: "we don't shit in our own yard").
test-*/
.test-*/
temp-*/
lint_out*
review-*.md
uat_verify*.sh
*.bak
*.tmp

# Agent artifacts that leak into root
*.db
*.sqlite
*-report.txt
*-output.txt
uat-*.json
lint.txt
lint-report.txt

# R004: Personal shell scripts — not part of gwrk distribution
scripts/dev/
.gwrk/dispatches.jsonl

.antigravitycli/
.antigravitycli/

# random files
*.err
*.out
# agent worktrees / local session state
.claude/
